{
  "title": "Smoky Chinese Dried White Navy Beans Stew",
  "description": "A rich, slow-cooked stew featuring tender dried white navy beans with a hint of smokiness from dried chili flakes and aromatic spices. High-protein and perfect for a hearty dinner.",
