  "instructions": [
    "Soak dried white navy beans overnight in water.",
    "In a large pot, sauté pork shoulder cubes with garlic and ginger until lightly browned.",
    "Add star anise, dried chili flakes, soy sauce, brown sugar, and 1 cup water. Bring to a gentle simmer.",
    "Add soaked beans and coconut milk. Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low.",
    "Cover and cook for 1 hour, stirring occasionally to prevent sticking.",
    "Add remaining 1 cup water and simmer for another 20 minutes until beans are tender.",
    "Adjust seasoning with a pinch of salt and a splash of water if needed.",
    "Cook pork to an internal temperature of 63°C / 145°F and let it rest for 3 minutes before serving."
  ],
